    {
      "id": "YP_TRANS_OLD_AGE",
      "category": "life.transition",
      "version": 1,
      "weight": 30,
      "kind": "decision",
      "conditions": {
        "regions": ["yellow_plains"],
        "minAge": 60
      },
      "timeCost": "LONG",
      "text": {
        "intro": [
          "The years have thinned the hands to paper, the breath to a rumour, the sight to the soft pale shapes of a world that no longer needs to be looked at clearly to be known. The kang is warm. The lamp is low. The house is quiet."
        ],
        "body": [
          "Outside in the lane a child is calling another child. The sound comes through the paper window the way water comes through a cupped hand — softened, beautiful, inexact. $[CHARACTER] lies on the kang and watches the shadow of a roof-beam that has held the roof up since long before memory.",
          "There is the small choice that the dying are sometimes given by their own bodies — to let the breath simply grow small and to be carried out by it, or to gather what is left of the will and reach, one last time, for something the long life kept trying to grasp. The qi at the dantian is a small ember, no longer warm. It could be banked or it could be spent. There is a third path, the oldest one: to call for the family, to put one's small accounting in order with the people who will remain."
        ]
      },
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ch_rest_peaceful",
          "label": "Rest. Let the breath grow small. The lamp burns down on its own.",
          "timeCost": "LONG",
          "outcomes": {
            "SUCCESS": {
              "narrativeKey": "reflection.mood.serenity.2",
              "stateDeltas": [
                { "kind": "insight_delta", "amount": 3 },
                { "kind": "flag_set", "flag": "died_peacefully" }
              ],
              "deathCause": "old_age"
            },
            "FAILURE": {
              "narrativeKey": "reflection.mood.serenity.2",
              "stateDeltas": [
                { "kind": "insight_delta", "amount": 3 },
                { "kind": "flag_set", "flag": "died_peacefully" }
              ],
              "deathCause": "old_age"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "ch_final_meditation",
          "label": "Gather what is left. Reach, one last time, for the breakthrough that was never granted.",
          "timeCost": "LONG",
          "check": { "base": 15, "stats": { "Spirit": 1, "Mind": 1 }, "difficulty": 60 },
          "outcomes": {
            "CRIT_SUCCESS": {
