    {
      "id": "YP_TRANS_CHILDBIRTH",
      "category": "life.transition",
      "version": 1,
      "weight": 8,
      "kind": "decision",
      "conditions": {
        "regions": ["yellow_plains"],
        "minAge": 18,
        "characterFlags": {
          "require": ["married"]
        }
      },
      "timeCost": "MEDIUM",
      "text": {
        "intro": [
          "A long night. The midwife — Old Mother Liu, who has done this for forty years and knows all the small signs no diagram in any text would record — kneels at the kang's edge with sleeves rolled back. The water is boiling on the stove. The moon is at the paper window, full and very white."
        ],
        "body": [
          "$[CHARACTER]'s body has been doing the work for sixteen hours. The pain is no longer something separate from the body; the body is the pain, and the breath is the body's small attempt to keep itself together inside the storm.",
          "The midwife mutters that the baby is turned wrong. There is, in such cases, the choice the family is asked to make on behalf of the labouring woman, since the labouring woman has long since stopped being able to make it for herself. The slow careful path: trust the midwife, trust the body, and risk the long dangerous turning. The forced path: a cut, a fast extraction, a wound that will or will not heal. The third path, ancient and grim: pray to the mother goddesses and let the body decide on its own, taking what comes."
        ]
      },
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ch_trust_midwife",
          "label": "Trust the midwife's hands. Slowly turn the child.",
          "timeCost": "MEDIUM",
          "check": { "base": 25, "stats": { "Spirit": 1, "Body": 1 }, "difficulty": 50 },
          "outcomes": {
            "CRIT_SUCCESS": {
              "narrativeKey": "emotion.hope.dawn",
              "stateDeltas": [
                { "kind": "flag_set", "flag": "has_child" },
                { "kind": "insight_delta", "amount": 5 },
                { "kind": "karma_delta", "amount": 2 }
              ]
            },
            "SUCCESS": {
              "narrativeKey": "emotion.hope.dawn",
              "stateDeltas": [
                { "kind": "flag_set", "flag": "has_child" },
                { "kind": "insight_delta", "amount": 3 }
              ]
            },
            "PARTIAL": {
              "narrativeKey": "emotion.hope.small",
              "stateDeltas": [
                { "kind": "flag_set", "flag": "has_child" },
                { "kind": "hp_delta", "amount": -5 },
                { "kind": "insight_delta", "amount": 2 }
              ]
            },
